  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个铸造交易的时序图。流程是：客户端发起请求，比如铸造NFT，然后系统先检查资格，不合格的直接拒绝，合格的进入异步处理，最后通过web socket通知结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Request Handler",
        "mint",
        "web socket"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到有两个分支：资格检查失败返回405，成功返回202并订阅web socket。异步处理部分需要几个参与者？数据库和处理器要分开画吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Request Handler",
        "Database Queue",
        "Request Processor",
        "405 Not allowed",
        "202 Accepted"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，需要分开。请求处理器把交易存到数据库队列，然后处理器拉取交易执行，最后由通知器统一推送给客户端。这样结构更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Request Handler",
        "Database Queue",
        "Request Processor",
        "Notifier"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了主体流程。Client发送请求到Request Handler，内部检查资格，alt分支处理两种结果。合格的路径：返回202 Accepted，同时订阅web socket，然后存储到Database Queue。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Request Handler",
        "Database Queue",
        "alt",
        "202 Accepted",
        "web socket"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "前半部分没问题。后半段呢？处理器和通知器的交互要体现异步特性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Request Processor",
        "Notifier"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。Database Queue把交易推给Request Processor处理，处理完成后通知Notifier，最后Notifier通过web socket告诉Client交易已完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Database Queue",
